# Neighborhood Krew Inc — Demo (Vite + React + Tailwind)

## Local dev
```bash
npm i
npm run dev
```

## Build & Preview
```bash
npm run build
npm run preview
```

## Vercel
- Framework Preset: **Vite**
- Build Command: `npm run build`
- Output Directory: `dist`

### Logo
Put your final file at `public/logokrew.png`, then set `LOGO_URL = "/logokrew.png"` in `src/App.tsx`.

/** @type {import('tailwindcss').Config} */
